TITLE      Cross section measurement of the 6Li(n,t)4He reaction
           in the MeV neutron energy range
AUTHOR     (Yu.M.Gledenov,I.Chuprakov,Guohui Zhang,G.Khuukhenkhuu,
           M.Odsuren,B.Usukhbayar,L.Krupa,E.Sansarbayar,Jie Liu,
